description: The Acaistas at Mahalo Bowl specialize in making healthy and delicious Acai bowls and smoothies that serve as a meal replacement, post workout meal or simply an energizing snack. Their bowls are all-natural, with no added sugar and certainly no high fructose corn syrup. As a result, these delicious bowls fill you up but never slow you down. So, the next time you see Mahalo Bowl in your neighborhood stop by and say hello!
name: Mahalo Bowl
